title: Cream Caramel Chocolate
original_name: クリームキャラメルショコラ
sinopse:
From Aerandria Scans:

Actually, Mikoto, a high school student who lives alone in an old apartment, just started dating Murakami-san, a university student who lives in the next room. Living under one roof, she's happy that she can be lovey-dovey every day with her boyfriend, but reality is somewhat different...
